# Frontend React

- Functional components; reusable logic in `src/hooks/` (e.g. `useDebouncedSave`).
- Use shadcn primitives from `@/components/ui`; extend via `cn()`, avoid forking shadcn files.
- Convex: `useQuery`, `useMutation`, `usePaginatedQuery` from `convex/react` — no raw fetch to Convex.
- Routes: `/` dashboard, `/contracts/:id` editor.
- Strict TypeScript; no `any`.
